    "_postman_id": "cms-users-api-collection",
    "name": "CMS - User Management API",
    "description": "User Management API collection for the Clinic Management System with Clean Architecture.\n\n## ðŸ‘¥ User Management API (/api/users)\n\nThis collection focuses specifically on user management endpoints:\n\n- **User CRUD Operations**: Create, read, update, and delete user accounts\n- **Password Management**: Change passwords with validation\n- **Role-Based Operations**: Filter and manage users by roles (admin, doctor, receptionist)\n- **User Profile Management**: Update user profile information\n- **Account Status**: Activate, deactivate, and manage user account status\n- **User Search**: Advanced user search and filtering capabilities\n- **Bulk Operations**: Manage multiple users efficiently\n\n## Testing Coverage\n\n- âœ… User creation with role assignment\n- âœ… User retrieval (single and list)\n- âœ… User profile updates\n- âœ… Password change functionality\n- âœ… Role-based filtering and operations\n- âœ… User account status management\n- âœ… User search and filtering\n- âœ… Error handling (validation, not found, duplicates)\n- âœ… Role validation and permissions\n- âœ… Bulk user operations\n\n## Environment Variables\n\nThis collection uses the following environment variables:\n- `cms_local`: http://localhost:4000 (for local development)\n- `cms_prod`: https://capstone-api.up.railway.app (for production)\n- `baseUrl`: Base URL for API endpoints\n- `authToken`: JWT token for authenticated requests\n- Various test data variables for dynamic testing",
